PersonalMission.Name: LT-10: The Best Result
PersonalMission.Description: The more effective you are in a battle, the more experience you will earn. Show them what a light tank is capable of!
PersonalMission.Hint: A good scout knows when to be cautious and when to be aggressive. Stay alert to the flow of battle.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Finish the battle as the top player on both teams by experience earned
•  Survive
